high_descs: Walk over to the microwave, then turn right and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the potato out of the sink.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the potato inside then close the door, heat up the potato for a couple seconds in the microwave then take it out and close the microwave.
Turn right to face the sink.
Put the heated potato into the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the sink.

high_descs: take the potato from the sink
take the potato to the sink
put the potato in the sink
anns.task_desc: warm a potato in the microwave then put it in the sink

high_descs: Walk forward to the stove top, then turn right and walk to the sink.
Pick up the potato from the sink.
Heat the potato in the microwave for a few seconds, then take it out and close the microwave.
Put the potato into the sink basin, in front of the spoon laying horizontally.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot potato in a sink basin.
